{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Hide the body \u2014 be fast and clever!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Think you\u2019ve got what it takes to outsmart the law? Where will you hide the body? Under the bed? Too easy. In a time machine? Now you\u2019re thinking!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405120/extras/4.gif?t=1738168266\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>PHYSICS AND CHAOS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Lift, drag, and get messy to hide the corpse \u2014 time\u2019s ticking, and the cops are coming!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405120/extras/3.gif?t=1738168266\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>IMPROVE YOUR STRATEGY</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Didn\u2019t nail it the first time? No problem! Go back, switch up your tactics, and discover new, smarter ways to hide the evidence. Every failure brings you closer to perfection!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405120/extras/2.gif?t=1738168266\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>AMAZING LOCATIONS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each level brings a fresh challenge:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Apartment:</strong> Find clever hiding spots in a familiar setting.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Museum:</strong> Conceal the body among art and exhibits.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Spaceship:</strong> Master zero-gravity chaos.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Sunken Ship:</strong> Submerge evidence and manipulate time.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">And more!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405120/extras/1.gif?t=1738168266\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>MAKE IT YOUR STYLE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Earn points by hiding evidence and erasing fingerprints, then spend them to unlock quirky skins like Zombie, Superhero, Disco, and more!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>DON\u2019T FORGET:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You have 4 minutes, 6 hiding spots, and a ticking clock before the cops arrive. Can you pull it off in time?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Get ready for epic chaos. And remember: time waits for no one!</strong> \ud83d\udea8</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405120/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738168266","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405120/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1738168266","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405120/65aac16f203c3513026a7b96cc78ea9846653578/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738168266","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405120/65aac16f203c3513026a7b96cc78ea9846653578/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1738168266","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Hide the body \u2014 be fast and clever!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Think you\u2019ve got what it takes to outsmart the law? Where will you hide the body? Under the bed? Too easy. In a time machine? Now you\u2019re thinking!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405120/extras/4.gif?t=1738168266\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>PHYSICS AND CHAOS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Lift, drag, and get messy to hide the corpse \u2014 time\u2019s ticking, and the cops are coming!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store